# Take different kinds of payment

In addition to card-based payments, you can take the following other kinds of payment with GOV.UK Pay:

* [digital wallet](/take_different_kinds_of_payment/digital_wallets/#take-digital-wallet-payments) payments
* [payments over the phone](/take_different_kinds_of_payment/moto_payments/#take-payments-over-the-phone-moto-payments) ('MOTO' payments)
* [Direct Debit](/take_different_kinds_of_payment/direct_debit/#take-direct-debit-payments) payments
